 Channel Water Balance

  Inflow  = Total inflow above channel outlet, includes baseflow, all sources m^3
  Outflow = Water flow out of channel outlet, m^3
  Storage = Water surface storage at the end of the day, m^3
  Baseflow = Portion of inflow from baseflow, m^3
  Loss = Transmission loss in channel, infiltration, m^3
  Balance = Water balance error at end of day, 0=balanced m^3
     inflow-outflow-loss-(change in surface storage)

